title: (VIDEO) Donald Trump Travels To Mexico: Is He Being Set Up? | Tom Sullivan Radio Show
text:
Tom Sullivan Aug 31, 2016 Donald Trump has a YUGE day ahead of him! Hours before his big primetime immigration policy speech, Donald Trump is scheduled to meet with Mexican President Enrique Peña Nieto? But will the high profile foreign policy photo op help him? Or could it backfire? Some pundits think so. If former Mexican President Vincente Fox’s reaction is any indication, he might not to get accepted with open arms when he lands south of the border.
